# Never 172 WSL/Docker as server IP

**Disc:** `docs/MOB-DISC-NO-WSL-172-AS-SERVER-IP.md`

- Never tell user to use `172.17`–`172.31` for dashboard / SIP / PTT
- Real Wi‑Fi/Ethernet only (lab example: `192.168.1.38`)
- Auto IP detect must use `Get-UbitronPreferredLanIPv4.ps1` (skip WSL/vEthernet/Docker)
- If unsure → ask which Wi‑Fi IP — do **not** guess 172
